<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Second Reception / Regional Reception</title>
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="styles.css">
  <link rel="stylesheet" href="https://cdnjs.cloudflare.com/ajax/libs/font-awesome/6.5.0/css/all.min.css">
</head>
<body>
  <header>
    <section class="hero-secondrecepp">
      <div class="hero-content-secondrecepp">
        <h1>Second Reception / Regional Reception</h1>
        <h2>"A Celebration Continued"</h2>
        <p> A warm and joyful extension of love, laughter, and togetherness.</p>
    
      </div>
    </section>
  </header>

  <main>
    <section class="description-secondrecepp" id="more">
      <p>
        Not everyone can make it to the main wedding celebration-but love has no boundaries. That’s why we’re oraganizing a Second Reception. That's a heartfelt gathering dedicated to your cherished friends and family who couldn’t attend the original event.
      </p>
    </section>

    <section class="features-secondrecepp">
      <div class="card-secondrecepp">
        <img src="/img/img (5).jpg" alt="Venue">
        <h3>Venue</h3>
        <h5><i>Choose a location that brings everyone together.</i></h5>
        <p>Find a space that fits your celebration-whether it's intimate or grand. Your venue sets the tone, so pick a place that feels just right for your second reception.

        </p>
        <a class="btn-secondrecepp" href="/hotels">Booking Venues</a>
      </div>
      <div class="card-secondrecepp">
        <img src="/img/dress_code.jpg" alt="Dress Code Themes">
        <h3>Dress Code Themes</h3>
        <h5><i>Set the mood with the perfect dress code.</i></h5>
        <p>Give your guests guidance on what to wear-formal, semi-formal, or themed. Keep it relaxed, fun, or fancy-your choice!

        </p>
        <a class="btn-secondrecepp" href="/dresses">Check Dress Code Themes</a>
      </div>
      <div class="card-secondrecepp">
        <img src="/img/theme.jpeg" alt="Event Themes">
        <h3>Event Themes</h3>
        <h5><i>Give your reception its own unique vibe.</i></h5>
        <p>
            From rustic charm to modern elegance, select a theme that reflects your style. Themes help tie together decorations, invites, and guest experience.
        </p>
       
      </div>
      <div class="card-secondrecepp">
        <img src="/img/games.jpeg" alt="Fun Games & Challenges">
        <h3>Fun Games & Challenges</h3>
        <h5><i>Keep guests engaged and entertained.</i></h5>
        <p>
            Add ice-breakers, trivia, challenges, or just fun games to get everyone laughing and interacting. Customize your event flow with playful moments. 
        </p>
       
      </div>

      <div class="card-secondrecepp">
        <img src="/img/decorations.jpeg" alt="Decorations">
        <h3>Decorations</h3>
        <h5><i>Design a space that tells your story.</i></h5>
        <p>
            Pick color palettes, floral arrangements, table settings, and more. Whether it's DIY or professionally done, great decor sets the mood.
        </p>
        <a class="btn-secondrecepp" href="/decorators">Explore Decoration Ideas</a>
      </div>

      <div class="card-secondrecepp">
        <img src="/img/foods.jpg" alt="Food & Drinks">
        <h3>Food & Drinks</h3>
        <h5><i>Plan a menu everyone will remember.</i></h5>
        <p>Choose between catering, buffet, or custom food stations. Add drink options and dessert ideas to round out your celebration.
            
        </p>
        <a class="btn-secondrecepp" href="catering">Check Food & Drinks</a>
      </div>

      <div class="card-secondrecepp">
        <img src="/img/dj.jpeg" alt="Entertainment">
        <h3>Entertainment</h3>
        <h5><i>Create a vibe with music and performances.</i></h5>
        <p>Add a DJ, live music, or a playlist to keep energy flowing. Entertainment helps transform your reception into a true celebration.
            
        </p>
        <a class="btn-secondrecepp" href="entertainment">Explore Entertainment Ideas</a>
      </div>
    </section>
  </main>
</body>
</html>
